.TH "vmw_du_helper_plane_update" 9 "vmw_du_helper_plane_update" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
vmw_du_helper_plane_update \- Helper to do plane update on a display unit.
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" vmw_du_helper_plane_update
.BI "(struct vmw_du_update_plane *update "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "update" 12
The closure structure.
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Call this helper after setting callbacks in \fIvmw_du_update_plane\fP to do plane
update on display unit.
.SH "RETURN"
0 on success or a negative error code on failure.
